<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Security & IT Readiness</h1>

  <p class="mb-4">
    <%= link_to 'replicate.info', root_path, class: "text-blue-600 font-semibold" %> is email-based by design. No dashboards, no logins, no integrations, no SSO. The architecture minimizes risk, and follows modern security practices without any complexity.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    The platform was designed by <%= link_to 'Jacob Comer', 'https://linkedin.com/in/jacobcomer', class: "text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition" %>, a Staff Engineer with 15 years of experience. He most recently led IAM for an infra/security market leader, and spent over a decade building enterprise software for regulated environments.
  </p>

  <p class="text-sm bg-neutral-100 p-2 text-center border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm leading-relaxed">
    Contact <%= mail_to 'security@replicate.info', 'security@replicate.info', class: "text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition" %> if you have questions, or want to request <%= link_to "our DPA", "/dpa.pdf", class: "text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition" %> (via DocuSign).
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-10 mt-14">

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-2xl tracking-tight">Architecture</h2>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Hosted on Heroku (AWS)</h3>
      <p>All infrastructure runs on isolated US cloud resources, with encrypted storage and enforced HTTPS.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Data encrypted in transit and at rest</h3>
      <p>All data is encrypted at rest using AES-256, managed by Heroku's infrastructure.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">No access to your customers' data</h3>
      <p>The platform does not integrate with your internal systems. It sends coaching emails to your engineers and helps them think through production risks. We persist your team's conversation history (for personalized coaching insights), and automatically delete that data within 12 months.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-2xl tracking-tight">Access & Delivery</h2>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">No user accounts or logins</h3>
      <p>Coaching is delivered by email. No sessions, passwords, or user-managed devices.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">No integrations required</h3>
      <p>We do not connect to GitHub, Jira, Slack, SMTP servers, or any other internal tool.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">You own your data</h3>
      <p>Coaching conversation history is only retained for up to 12 months to personalize future learning sessions. You can permanently delete all of your organization's data at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:support@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition">support@replicate.info</a>.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Planned shutdowns</h3>
      <p>In the case of a planned end-of-service, customers would receive advance notice and a downloadable archive of recent coaching history, prompts, and full source code. Support would remain available through the shutdown window.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Provisioning and SCIM</h3>
      <p>SCIM is planned for early 2026. Admins currently manage employee access by emailing <a href="mailto:support@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition">support@replicate.info</a>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-2xl tracking-tight">Compliance</h2>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">DPA available</h3>
      <p>Contact <%= mail_to 'security@replicate.info', 'security@replicate.info', class: "text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition" %> if you have questions, or want to request <%= link_to "our DPA", "/dpa.pdf", class: "text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition" %> (via DocuSign).</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">SOC 2 Type 1 planned for 2026</h3>
      <p>Documentation is available for teams evaluating vendor readiness.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">No redlines</h3>
      <p>Our documents are standardized and public. No vendor portals, no negotiation loops.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-2xl tracking-tight">Subprocessors</h2>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">
        All vendors below support GDPR compliance and offer Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs) where required.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Heroku (AWS)</h3>
      <p>Used for infrastructure and encrypted storage. All workloads run in isolated dynos with HTTPS enforced and AES-256 encryption at rest.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">OpenAI</h3>
      <p>We use OpenAI's API for real-time content generation for coaching emails. None of your data is persisted by OpenAI, and none of it is used to train their models. The prompting is completely ephemeral. Enterprise customers may request alternate LLM providers if required by internal policy.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Postmark</h3>
      <p>Used for transactional email delivery. No open or click tracking is enabled.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Stripe</h3>
      <p>Used for payment processing and invoicing.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Google Analytics</h3>
      <p>Used to measure basic marketing website traffic. No tracking occurs inside coaching flows or emails.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <p class="text-gray-500 mt-10">
    <%= link_to 'Terms of Service', '/terms', class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %> &nbsp;&nbsp;â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <%= link_to 'Privacy Policy', '/privacy', class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %>
  </p>
</div>